Resources
0. Home
1. Session 
2. User
3. Characters
4. Groups

HOME CONTROLLER
/ (GET) // this is the homepage

SESSION CONTROLLER

API:
api/login (POST) // authenticates credentials against database and either redirects home with a new session or redirects back to /login
api/logout (POST) // destroys session and redirects to previous webpage

FRONTEND:
/login (GET) // gets the webpage that has the login form
/logout (GET) // logout webpage

USER CONTROLLER

API
api/users/{id}/favs (GET) //
api/users/{id}/favs (POST) //
api/users/{id}/favs/{idCharacter} (DELETE) //

FRONTEND
/user/{id} (GET)
/user (POST)
/users/{id} (GET)
/register (GET)  // gets the webpage that has the registration form
/users/{id}/favs (GET)

CHARACTER CONTROLLER

API:
api/characters
api/character/{id} (POST)
api/ranking

FRONTEND:

/characters (GET) // displays all marvel characters
/ranking (GET) // pantalla de characters ordenada por cantidad de favoritos


GROUP CONTROLLER
API:
api/groups (GET)
api/groups (POST)

api/groups/{id} (GET)
api/groups/{id} (PUT)
api/groups/{id} (DELETE)

FRONTEND:
/groups (GET) //
/groups/{id} (GET)
